Hello,

We are so exited to announce the launch of our new website, online store and a newsletter!

At our website you can now browse entire catalogs of the brands that we carry at our optical store, order online or share the glasses that you like with your friends!
You can also sign up for an eye exam online and see our optometrist's schedule. This makes us the largest fashion brand name online glasses store in Ontario! 

We operate in a high fashion industry and carry most of world's best eyeglasses brands. Prada, Bvlgari, Tom Ford, Tiffany, Gucci, Dior plus 40 more famous and niche brands.
With the help of our new website, we will be sharing with you interesting news and trends as they are happening in the fashion world. We promise to e-mail you only when there is something exciting to share!

To make things more interesting, we some times have limited time offers, promotions and coupons.

We are looking forward to service your vision needs.

We would like to invite you to join our Facebook page and would appreciate your share to help us grow our business:
https://www.facebook.com/IlluminataEyewear

We are looking forward to seeing you soon at our store!


